Kim Milford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kim_Milford 0 Richard Kim Milford (February 7, 1951 – June 16, 1988), known professionally as Kim Milford, was an American actor, singer-songwriter, and composer. He is known for his stage acting in musicals such as The Rocky Horror Show and Jesus Christ Superstar.
